title: Bobby’s Christmas Surprise Ruined! + Amy Saw A Legendary Country Artist Doing Their Own Grocery Shopping + Lunchbox on Why America Has Gone To Crap
itunes:title: Bobby’s Christmas Surprise Ruined! + Amy Saw A Legendary Country Artist Doing Their Own Grocery Shopping + Lunchbox on Why America Has Gone To Crap
description:
Bobby talks about his big Christmas surprise to his fiancé Caitlin…and how it got ruined. He’s wondering now if he still has to get her a Christmas gift on top of the ruined one. Bobby gives Lunchbox 60 seconds to rant about why he thinks American has gone to crap.
